        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "他們就彼此議論：“如果我們說‘是從天上來的’，他就會說‘那你們為甚麼不信他呢？’"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "他們彼此商議說：「我們若說『從天上來』，他必說：『這樣，你們為甚麼不信他呢？』"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "They began reasoning among themselves, saying, “If we say, ‘From heaven,’ He will say, ‘Then why did you not believe him?’"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "They discussed it among themselves and said, “If we say, ‘From heaven,’ he will ask, ‘Then why didn’t you believe him?’"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "They talked it over among themselves. “If we say it was from heaven, he will ask why we didn’t believe John."
      }
